d, binary builds and runs successfully\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**Total Tasks**: 20\n**Estimated Effort**: M (Medium) - 8-12 hours\n\n### Key Deliverables\n1. **Server framework** - Complete HTTP server with lifecycle management\n2. **Router** - RESTful API routing for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n3. **Middleware system** - Logging, recovery, CORS, metrics, request ID\n4. **Handlers** - CRUD handlers for both resource types\n5. **Health checks** - Liveness and readiness probes\n6. **Error handling** - Unified error responses and K8s error conversion\n7. **Metrics** - Prometheus metrics integration\n8. **Configuration** - Environment variable and config file support\n9. **Tests** - Comprehensive unit and integration tests\n10. **Documentation** - API documentation and usage guide\n\n### Success Criteria\n- All unit tests pass with >80% code coverage\n- All integration tests pass\n- Server starts and stops gracefully\n- Health checks respond correctly\n- All CRUD operations work for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n- Error handling returns appropriate HTTP status codes\n- Metrics are properly recorded\n- Code passes static analysis and linting\n- Documentation is complete and accurate\n\n### Dependencies\n- Go 1.24+\n- Kubernetes cluster (for testing)\n- gorilla/mux router\n- Prometheus client library\n- k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1\n- k8s.io/api v0.34.1\n\n### Blocked By\n- None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n\n### Blocks\n- AR-001 (AgentRuntime Controller) - may use workloadmanager HTTP API\n- AR-002 (CodeInterpreter Controller) - may use workloadmanager HTTP API\n- AR-005 (Agent Integration) - will use workloadmanager HTTP API","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md","exists":true,